title: Talks
name: Appraisal Talk on Disaster Risk Reduction: Landslides
about: Landslides gave chills and thrills to campus commuters for the last 3 months. While sir responded to a few-many calls, emails, and other means, sir wanted to address the general audience on technical aspects of Landslide.

title: Event
name: AutoCAD Learning Series & Competition
about: In this learning series, we will help beginners and anyone seeking a refresher course by teaching you how to make computer-aided designs of different structures. We will cover drawing, taking measurements, producing templates, and everything required to generate professional designs.
